window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><i>Died for a cause</i>.</p> <p>Johnny’s tombstone would read like something you’d find in a dime novel at a used bookstore. Going out like a snuffed candle, his life ended just as it had really begun.</p> <p>Now he’s been given a second chance to fight his way out of the corner he put himself into.</p> <p>In a world of brawls, dirty fights, and hard-hitting cultivators, he must win. Because if he loses, he’ll lose more than just the fight, and it won’t be his life. He already managed that once, after all.</p> <p><b>Warning:</b> This slice-of-life, slow-burn, gamelit story contains adult themes, undefined relationships/harem, and graphic violence.</p>"; 
